\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{Y}(y)=f_{X}\left[h(y)\right]\left|\frac{\partial h(y)}{y}\right|\text{ for }\mbox{\alpha<y<\beta}
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $(\alpha,\beta)$
\end_inset

 is the mapped interval from 
\begin_inset Formula $(a,b)$
\end_inset

.
